item.title: Made a no-ip account, now what?
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

PortForwarding.
Go to www.portforward.com
Click ‘PortForwarding’ at the top of the page
Select your router from the list
Select the program you are PortForwarding for, choose the first option; ‘First SMTP server’
Follow the tutorial on PortForwarding your router.
